OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783975667
OL,3,CTeenagers urged to get meningitis B
OL,4,Cjab before going to university
OL,6,FHundreds of thousands of teenagers in
OL,7,FEngland are being urged to book
OL,8,Fmeningitis B vaccine appointments
OL,9,Fbefore they go to university in the
OL,10,Fautumn.
OL,12,FYear 13 pupils aged 17 and 18 will be
OL,13,Feligible for the one-off jab
OL,14,Fprogramme, with two doses given at
OL,15,Fleast 28 days apart, with the rollout
OL,16,Fbeginning on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
