PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783975667
OL,3,CTeenagers urged to get meningitis B
OL,4,Cjab before going to university
OL,6,FPeople under 25 who are going to
OL,7,Funiversity or other residential
OL,8,Ffurther education in the autumn will
OL,9,Falso be eligible and can book their
OL,10,Fappointments, which start from July 20.
OL,12,FThe vaccination programme was
OL,13,Fannounced by the government last month
OL,14,Fafter a series of meningitis
OL,15,Foutbreaks, the most serious of which
OL,16,Fwas in Kent and left two teenagers
OL,17,Fdead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
