OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783975667
OL,3,CTeenagers urged to get meningitis B
OL,4,Cjab before going to university
OL,6,FMenB is a serious infection that can
OL,7,Fbe fatal and progresses rapidly. The
OL,8,Fbacteria that cause the illness are
OL,9,Fspread through close contact, such as
OL,10,Fkissing, sharing drinks or living in
OL,11,Fhalls of residence.
OL,13,FThe risk of MenB for first-year
OL,14,Funiversity students is about seven
OL,15,Ftimes higher than people of a similar
OL,16,Fage who did not go to university,
OL,17,Faccording to NHS England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
