PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783975667
OL,3,CTeenagers urged to get meningitis B
OL,4,Cjab before going to university
OL,6,FDr Shamez Ladhani, consultant
OL,7,Fepidemiologist at the UK Health
OL,8,FSecurity Agency, said: "The risk of
OL,9,FMenB rises sharply for young people
OL,10,Fstarting university, where mixing
OL,11,Fclosely with so many new people
OL,12,Fincreases exposure to the bacteria.
OL,14,F"Getting both doses of the vaccine
OL,15,Fover the summer will provide robust
OL,16,Fprotection against most meningococcal
OL,17,Fstrains, offering vital peace of mind
OL,18,Ffor students and families as they take
OL,19,Fthis next big step."
OL,26,@pD@XOUvD@AOU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
