OL,3,CTeenagers urged to get meningitis B
OL,4,Cjab before going to university
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FBrian Davies, head of health insights
OL,12,Fand policy at Meningitis Research
OL,13,FFoundation, said: "Too many of the
OL,14,Fpeople we support are left asking
OL,15,F'what if?' after MenB has changed
OL,16,Ftheir lives forever.
OL,18,F"This vaccination programme gives
OL,19,Fyoung people and their families the
OL,20,Fchance to avoid that heartbreak."
OL,26,@uD@SOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
