PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1783975667
OL,3,CTeenagers urged to get meningitis B
OL,4,Cjab before going to university
OL,6,FIt comes as the Department of Health
OL,7,Fand Social Care and the Department for
OL,8,FEducation launched a school-aged
OL,9,Fvaccination taskforce in a bid to
OL,10,Fimprove uptake of jabs.
OL,12,FThe Joint Committee on Vaccination and
OL,13,FImmunisation is also currently looking
OL,14,Fat whether a bigger and longer
OL,15,Fprogramme is needed for young people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
